Four Exhibitions opened on October 17, 2014.  Story Quilts by Marion Coleman; Landscape Revisited by Martin Weinstein, Sandra Gottlieb, Jonathan Beer (organized by Katharine T. Carter &amp; Assoc.);  Looking Through to the Past by C.A. Fuhs, historical photos of Wichita Falls (1876-1963); Quilting Wichita Falls Together, a community project funded by The Priddy Foundation
A few photos from the Opening Reception October 17th.
